There are multiple Christmas markets in Strasbourg. The picture is of Place Broglie (next to the Opera House) about 500m from the nearest place mentioned in the description of the attack (Rue des Grandes Arcades). The filename correctly already included Place Broglie. It makes sense that all Christmas markets in Strasbourg were closed as a reaction to the attack.
